<h2>Minors</h2>
<ul>
	<li><a href="/ucat/colleges-depts/urban-planning-public-affairs/pa/minor-civic-analytics/">Minor in Civic Analytics</a></li>
	<li><a href="/ucat/colleges-depts/urban-planning-public-affairs/pa/minor-nonprofit-management">Minor in Nonprofit Management</a></li>
